<p>carrying at night from road dump to front line.</p>
<p>4th Sunday. June.<br/>Fritz shelled our trenches again hindering working parties. Exciting air duel on ending in one of Fritz's being brought down.</p>
<p>5th. Monday.<br/>Standtoo from 2.30 to 3.30am. now being daybreak very early. 7th Brigade raided enemy lines so we had to draw fire &amp; got it hot &amp; strong. Several killed &amp; wounded as result. 4 of my own platoon. Showery weather also.</p>
<p>6th. Tuesday.<br/>Fairly quiet day. Showery and Cold.</p>
<p>7th Wednesday.<br/>Repairing damaged trenches from bombardment.</p>
